<title>
Tire Inspection
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Check tires for uneven or excessive wear, or damage. If defective, replace tire.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Refer to 
<intxref refid = "AENCP70A2406002">Tire Inspection</intxref>
 for details.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH01020022.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "50.492mm" ver = "01" gw = "122" gh = "126"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "1.028in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
1.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Wear indicator
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Check inflation pressure of each tire and adjust pressure to specification if necessary.
</ptxt>
<attention3>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Tire inflation pressure should be checked when tires are cool.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Specified tire inflation pressure is indicated on the tire placard.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention3>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Rotate tires. For details, refer to 
<intxref refid = "AENCP70A2406005">Tire Rotation</intxref>
.
</ptxt>
</s1>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
